    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the roof, and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a persistent tear in the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind investing a little TLC.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, with no mechanical issues to report. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster and minor scuffing on the door panels. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, but you will find a few small stone chips on the front bumper and a minor scratch on the rear passenger door. Overall, it is a solid, well-kept car that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in true showroom condition. This meticulously preserved example displays an uncompromising level of care, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that remains in as-new condition. Every component has been maintained to the highest standards, ensuring a driving experience that is indistinguishable from the day it first rolled off the assembly line. For the collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than the absolute best, this vehicle stands as a benchmark of quality and long-term value.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I'm finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my weekend baby, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and pampered with hand washes only. Honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve looked it over top to bottom, and aside from a tiny, barely-there stone chip on the lower bumper that you'd need a magnifying glass to find, it\u2019s basically flawless. It drives like a dream\u2014smooth, tight, and plenty of heart. I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I do. Come by, let's grab a coffee and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "An absolute masterclass in analog performance. This 997-generation Carrera S features a 3.8L flat-six that has been maintained to a standard bordering on obsessive. The power delivery is surgically linear, benefiting from a high-flow intake plenum and a bespoke exhaust tuning that optimizes backpressure for peak mid-range torque. The chassis dynamics are razor-sharp, thanks to a suspension refresh utilizing stiffer bushings and adjustable drop links for zero-deflection at the apex. The aesthetic is equally flawless, with a deep multi-stage ceramic-coated finish that highlights the classic wide-body silhouette. Mechanically sound with documented compression tests and a reinforced IMS bearing, this is a turnkey specimen for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom ready. Better than new. Zero issues. Move fast.",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule of pure automotive elegance. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a legacy in motion. Draped in a shimmering coat of Brilliant Silver that seems to capture the very essence of the horizon, this masterpiece beckons for the long way home. Inside, the cabin welcomes you with the rich, unmistakable aroma of hand-finished leather and the tactile warmth of genuine walnut trim. Every curve of its iconic silhouette tells a story of sunset drives and the quiet confidence of a machine built to transcend eras. To sit behind the wheel is to command a symphony of precision and grace\u2014a rare opportunity to own a piece of rolling poetry that feels as vibrant and soul-stirring as the day it first graced the road.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
